The Chronicle Online Reporter Zanu-PF will on Wednesday convene an ordinary meeting of the Politburo at its headquarters in Harare. Secretary for Information and Publicity Cde Simon Khaya Moyo confirmed the meeting in a statement. “The Secretary for Administration Dr Obert Mpofu wishes to advise all members that there shall be a Politburo meeting to be held on Wednesday 4 December, 2019 at the party headquarters commencing at 1000 hours,” he said. 